name: Starbucks
directions: On far side from Lake Cook Rd; left bathroom has an infant changing table and right bathroom has a urinal.
comment: You can go in through the back (from the large parking lot) and end up right by the restrooms.

name: Jewel-Osco
directions: Walk in any door, go right all the way to photo counter/liquor section, bathrooms on far end of photo counter.
comment: Open 7 days a week till midnight, opens most days at 6am. - (847) 381-4525
